    "description": "Mitsubishi Pencil Co., Ltd. manufactures and supplies writing instruments in Japan, the United States, Europe, Asia, and internationally. The company operates through Writing Instruments and Writing Instrument Peripheral Products Business; and Other Business segments. It offers pencils and colored pencils, water-based ink roller balls, oil-based ballpoint pens, mechanical pencils and refill lead, felt-tip pens and markers, and office and school supplies; and the sale of adhesive tape and handicrafts. The company also provides ballpoint pen; multifunctional and customizable pen; sign pens and markers; seals and name pens; green net; and sharp; eye makeup and hair dye products; and carbon nanotubes, acoustic matching layers, electrode materials, and containers. It serves medical care, electronics, automobiles, and cosmetics industries. Mitsubishi Pencil Co., Ltd. was founded in 1887 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
